<br>
I have a quick question?  I am level 60 with epic and my question is this?  Is there any quests out there worth really doing for the Mage class?  I have started the Veracity earring quest but thats about all I can see worth while at this point?  Mabey I am missing something but it seems there really isn't great quests to do that is really beneficial to our class.  Am I correct in this assumption?<br>
<br>
If you know of a quest that is worth doing can you please share?  Sometimes I get bored and soloing takes its toll on me at times.  So id like something else to do while my guild is not raiding.  <br>
<br>
